If PRIVATE_SKIP_COMPILATION with no PRIVATE_TIDY_CHECKS, we'll only print this line in the build recipe?

1180:2-1180:50
Tue Apr 19 19:05:10 2016 +0000
Author: Chih-hung Hsieh <1052399@85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889>
Parent: 08fc147c_db775f5b
UUID: 68a590c6_054e566c
Bytes: 180
We print this line only if
 $(and $(PRIVATE_SKIP_COMPILATION),$(PRIVATE_TIDY_CHECKS)),

When compilation is not skipped normally, we print the normal compilation message as before.

